EXCLUSIVE 7-ELEVEN BANG ENERGY FLAVOR! 🍭

.

🛹 DROP-IN and grab this all NEW @BangEnergy and @7Eleven exclusive collab, Swirly Pop! Available only at 7-Eleven stores, this new flavor has the same 300 mg of caffeine to fuel your life but featuring a unique 7-Eleven flavor, there’s no doubt you’ll instantly know it and love it! 

.

Tag a friend that needs to try this gnarly new flavor!

.

Follow the inventor of Bang: @BangEnergy.CEO😎

.
